Class HexavigesimalDateFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.text.Format
      • java.text.DateFormat
        • com.mmm.cms.util.HexavigesimalDateFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class HexavigesimalDateFormat
extends java.text.DateFormat
    This formatter converts a Date to the day of the year consistent Hexavigesimal value. Any day of the year will be represented as the same value no matter what year that day belongs to.
    Author:
    3M Health Information Systems for CMS Home Health
